{"tid":376283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傻閪男女打風行山 累消防要上山營救","createTime":"2017-08-27T01:05:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T10:23:48.000Z","uid":23707,"like":4,"dislike":98,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b24b280388b3ff7962052de8be1b2fd077a89df","tid":376283,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T01:05:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170827/bkn-20170827083008554-0827_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170827%2Fbkn-20170827083008554-0827_00822_001.html&d=Z6mWvjkh4U%2FzXuqpUJjLFJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=3ef39587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170827/bkn-20170827083008554-0827_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n帕卡襲港下，一對男女昨日到黃大仙飛鵝山行山，至晚上7時47分，警方接報指2人被困山頭，於是聯同消防員等近百人登山拯救。至凌晨時份，首先將被困男子救出，由於出現低溫不適，需要送院。<br />\n<br />\n至於女事主因滑下百米深斜坡，腳部受傷，導致營救困難，消防小心翼翼游繩以下，陪伴在其身傍，但由於狂風大雨，山上環境惡劣，未能將她救離險地，只能夠取來毛氈為她保暖，通宵陪伴在山頭，至早上8時許，山上的救援人員亦難抵一晚風雨，需要通知上峰增援，要求調派近百張毛氈登山保暖。"},{"pid":"6b9cfa0952d2a96f89c53090f20813dd5147c0eb","tid":376283,"uid":68736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T01:07:00.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"14a79ef911a578653ebdbf59637db7b71db217d5","tid":376283,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T01:07:26.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2803692cfdf5181893f7301e4644e0a07ec71052","tid":376283,"uid":11995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T01:08:11.000Z","msg":"有無腦架屌你老母"},{"pid":"0f1b31a93c789311cb4c51f9ce9ffac6db6a698f","tid":376283,"uid":132039,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T01:09:06.000Z","msg":"唉，情況好惡劣，我d伙記仲係山未走得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee458ab9c8e9c9995829b1e65e167d2c6ec1c7a","tid":376283,"uid